snippet.title: Best VGM 929 - Dragon Quest VIII - Overture (Series' 25th Anniversary)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 73 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mg236zrHA40
Best VGM 2328 - https://youtu.be/I9mDBcDrwo4

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Dragon Quest VIII (2004)
Overture
Koichi Sugiyama
